999/2000 |first=Margaret |last=Sanger |authorlink=Margaret Sanger |work=The Margaret Sanger Papers |publisher=[[New York University]] |origyear=1999|year=2000 |accessdate=August 18, 2012}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"CFAM\">{{cite web |url=http://www.c-fam.org/docLib/20100924_6_more_problems_with_WD.pdf |title=Six More Problems with Women Deliver: Why Attempts to Redefine Maternal Health as Reproductive Health Threaten the World's Women |author=Foster, Catherine; Harrison, Donna J.; Melton, Grace; Pawloski, Amanda; Wright, Wendy; Yoshihara, Susan (editor) |publisher=[[Catholic Family and Human Rights Institute]] |date=August 20, 2010 |accessdate=August 18, 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121030132256/http://www.c-fam.org/docLib/20100924_6_more_problems_with_WD.pdf |archivedate=October 30, 2012}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Blog - Robles\">{{cite web|url=http://raissarobles.com/2012/08/17/update-senator-sotto-lifted-from-5-bloggers-and-1-briefing-paper/ |title=UPDATE: Senator Sotto lifted from 5 bloggers and 1 briefing paper |first=Raissa |last=Robles |work=Inside Philippine politics and beyond |date=August 17, 2012 |accessdate=August 18, 2012}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"WikiSource - PH Constitution\">{{cite wikisource |wslink=Constitution of the Philippines (1987) |plaintitle=Constitution of the Philippines |chapter=Article VI: Legislative Department |year= 1987}}</ref>\n}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.titosotto.com/ Tito Sotto Website]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20070429231244/http://www.eatbulaga.tv/home.htm Eat Bulaga! website]\n*[http://www.senate.gov.ph/senators/former_senators/vicente_sotto_iii.htm Official Senate Biography of Vicente C. Sotto III]\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-off}}\n{{s-bef|before=Elmer Pormiento}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Vice Mayor of Quezon City|years=1988\u20131992}}\n{{s-aft|after=Charito Planas}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Aquilino Pimentel, Jr.]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Minority Floor Leader of the Senate of the Philippines]]|years=2002\u20132004}}\n